text: Rosie Alice Huntington-Whiteley (born 18 April 1987) is an English movie actress and model. She is known for modeling for Victoria's Secret and in Burberry magazine. Her first movie was the 2011 action movie Transformers: Dark of the Moon. Huntington-Whiteley was born on 18 April 1987 in Plymouth, Devon, England. She has been partners with Jason Statham since 2010. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Devon Category:English models Category:English movie actors Category:People from Plymouth
